{"type": "article", "id": 63726, "title": "YouTube 推出 6 秒视频广告剪辑工具，肯德基歌单致敬嘻哈歌手 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-05-14T04:49:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11060, "name": "防晒"}, {"id": 6475, "name": "朋友圈"}, {"id": 16162, "name": "聚划算"}, {"id": 408, "name": "微信"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190514122939RiTst7HeNhGjQxYL.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"5Pux\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4371789654075928?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>马思纯成为珠宝品牌麒麟（Qeelin ）代言人，</b></a>品牌已经于 2013 年被开云集团收购。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190514123000J5I40NZrw16MgEen.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"xd38\"><a href=\"https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/harry-potter-x-vans-sneaker-collection-coming-soon-news.80011.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Vans x 哈利波特联名系列鞋款照露出。</b></a>看起来融入了格兰芬多院徽、预言家日报、斯莱特林蛇皮、金色飞贼等经典元素，目前还没有公布具体发售时间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905141230220q8Z7iLlXeauos6N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190514123021aGhmocX47gYw15sL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.164228\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905141230216jnRLl3soPpSUxEa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.066667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190514123022U4CMDcLi8pKe53tq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190514123023YBGIqP84LMDO7XnN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190514123023pfotQZjOhkEuy2WN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.134959\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190514123025wv21pQ7uTnqIS5BL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"NcLm\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/dhv5QVVa3HA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" savefrom_lm_index=\"0\" savefrom_lm=\"1\"><b>亚马逊 Prime 视频发布 2019 年 <i>Great shows stay with you</i>（精彩节目与你同在）系列作品。</b></a><span style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; margin-left: 5px;\"><a href=\"http://savefrom.net/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdhv5QVVa3HA&amp;utm_source=chameleon&amp;utm_medium=extensions&amp;utm_campaign=link_modifier\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Get a direct link\" savefrom_lm=\"1\" savefrom_lm_is_link=\"1\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;data:image/gif;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; width: 16px; height: 16px; display: inline-block; border: none; text-decoration: none; padding: 0px; position: relative;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a></span>短片展示人物在观看电视剧后的转变，剧集包括《了不起的麦瑟尔夫人》、《汉娜》、《医院革命》和《孤注一掷：曼彻斯特城》。创意代理商是 Droga5。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=n0870uynl6z\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x0870z97fs0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w0870m9ftol\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v0870chxdlz\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"zbk3\"><b><a href=\"https://youtu.be/9TO8i7W7dcI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" savefrom_lm_index=\"0\" savefrom_lm=\"1\">Sainsbury's 超市为纪念诞生 150 周年，发布广告片 <em>Proudly Doing Our Bit</em></a><span style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; margin-left: 5px;\"><a href=\"http://savefrom.net/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9TO8i7W7dcI&amp;utm_source=chameleon&amp;utm_medium=extensions&amp;utm_campaign=link_modifier\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Get a direct link\" savefrom_lm=\"1\" savefrom_lm_is_link=\"1\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;data:image/gif;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; width: 16px; height: 16px; display: inline-block; border: none; text-decoration: none; padding: 0px; position: relative;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a></span>。</b>片子通过一个奇幻的蛋糕回顾了 Sainsbury's 的历史，突出它济困和慈善传统。创意代理商是 W+K / 伦敦。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=h0870dvj38c\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"qXvM\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/creativity/kfc-made-a-spotify-playlist-of-bucket-bangers-46-hip-hop-tracks-that-referenced-the-brand/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>肯德基在 Spotify 上建了个 “Bucket Bangers”歌单，向嘻哈音乐致敬。</b></a>在过去 30 年里，肯德基曾被嘻哈歌手提到过 46 次。肯德基法国代理商 Sid Lee/巴黎还创建了户外广告，推广播放列表。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905141233536zaO7VyrFHw5q1oI.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583507\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905141233355pkNvnH6Vdjiu8LC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190514123333jvVSZdxK8JoWH41e.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.251111\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"23WR\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1721410501/4371455376467962\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>聚划算发布了支防晒浮云主题曲。</b></a>它找来音乐人王二狗创作演唱歌曲 “愿你如云般自在，终被温柔以待”，片中人造浮云提供防晒功能，推广大理欢聚日活动。此外，聚划算和暴龙、蕉下等防晒用具品牌举行云下音乐会。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=r0869a17ixu\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"M1SE\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5MzEzNDg3MQ==&amp;mid=2652769343&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=15e79c65c14a7f18317e3d8bd11374bf&amp;chksm=8b882547bcffac51bc637858fecbfc569039c1ffbf8578eb62296236e440cce8e5d8092cf583&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0514UfzlNOslwMqJv2PiOor9&amp;key=68edd2f2ad8b3fc0314fcb1857a5b301a3eae5ff858929d90e4d863a85a329674674c12140f9f1d3869128dc9a4fefb2787ec1549e0d9ea5a1c81c0c6aa2fb5ee62630c54f19545876fa3c7dc4efa93a&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=zQGXoX0XVK6vb%2Bw2bEq1cKYtFqGbAx0xKmhaet4WdiAjZH8IQ4eLTQR1djpoQgWq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>微信安全中心处理朋友圈利诱分享链接。</b></a>部分公众号、App 应用借返学费、送实物等方式，要求微信用户分享到朋友圈完成打卡，诱导分享并不是正常分享行为。微信对流利阅读、火箭单词、潘多拉英语和薄荷阅读点名，并且鼓励用户投诉。</p><p line=\"OjRy\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/youtube-is-pushing-six-second-ads-as-marketers-cool-on-the-format-2019-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>YouTube 推出 6 秒视频广告剪辑工具 Bumper Machine。</b></a>这一新工具最多能分析 90 秒的广告长度。不过 MediaRadar 的新研究发现，6 秒广告的客户同比下降了 20%，新广告形式正在失去广告主的青睐。</p><p line=\"nuEc\"><b><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/disney-consolidates-media-business-with-omd-following-20th-century-fox-acquisition/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">OMD 获得 20 世纪福克斯的美国媒介购买和规划业务</a>，</b>还负责漫威、皮克斯动画、福斯探照灯影业、20 世纪福克斯电影家庭娱乐以及即将推出的迪士尼+流媒体服务。之前福克斯的媒介业务由阳狮和 MDC Partners 负责。</p><p line=\"U3ds\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/brHzekoU56Y?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nathan Anderson</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/tan?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}